Task Description:
## Description
- add new hook to pre-commit to fix eof lines
- add new `release.yml` workflow. this workflow will automatically:
	- create and push new tag for next [semver based on conventional-commits](https://github.com/semantic-release/semantic-release#commit-message-format)
	- create GitHub release with notes
	- update Changelog with release notes
	- this workflow will also automatically notify PRs that are included in the release, mimicking the manual behavior but now its automated https://github.com/clowdhaus/terraform-aws-rds/pull/1#issuecomment-952097291
- remove old `chglog` configs and Makefile

## Motivation and Context
- automate release process in a standardized manner
- standardize new CI workflow (copying from RDS)

## Breaking Changes
- No

## How Has This Been Tested?
- [x] https://github.com/terraform-aws-modules/terraform-aws-rds/pull/361

